---
title: Cal Smart Asian-Style Pork Patties with Rice, Salad and DIY Honey-Sesame Dressing
description: These tender and flavourful pork patties are inspired by Japanese-style hamburger steaks. Accompanied by a fresh salad with juicy tomatoes, crunchy radishes and DIY honey-sesame dressing, this cozy meal will instantly transport your taste buds!
